<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="robots" content="noindex">
<title>Thanks for upgrading — DocKit Pro</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,500;9..144,600&family=Inter:wght@400;450;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --ink:#13211d;
  --ink-soft:#33473f;
  --paper:#F2F7F4;
  --paper-deep:#e6efea;
  --cream:#ffffff;
  --line:#d9e6df;
  --teal:#1D9E75;
  --teal-deep:#0f6e56;
  --teal-soft:#e3f4ed;
  --gold:#B8860B;
  --gold-soft:rgba(184,134,11,0.10);
  --muted:#6f7d77;
  --shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(19,33,29,.04), 0 8px 30px rgba(19,33,29,.07);
}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{
  font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
  background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);
  line-height:1.6;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:24px;
}
.display{font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1.1}

.card{
  width:100%;max-width:520px;
  background:var(--cream);
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:20px;
  padding:44px 40px 34px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  animation:rise .5s cubic-bezier(.16,.84,.44,1) both;
}
@keyframes rise{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}

.card::before{
  content:"";position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--teal),var(--teal-deep));
}

.eyebrow{
  font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--muted);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;margin-bottom:22px;
}
.status-dot{
  width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--teal);
  box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(29,158,117,.4);animation:pulse 2.4s infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse{
  0%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(29,158,117,.35)}
  70%{box-shadow:0 0 0 7px rgba(29,158,117,0)}
  100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(29,158,117,0)}
}

.check{
  width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--teal-soft);border:1px solid rgba(29,158,117,.3);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:22px;
}
.check svg{width:23px;height:23px;stroke:var(--teal-deep)}

h1{font-size:27px;margin-bottom:12px}
.lede{font-size:15.5px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:28px}

.steps-label{
  font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px;
}
ol.steps{list-style:none;counter-reset:step;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;margin-bottom:26px}
ol.steps li{
  counter-increment:step;display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;
  padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--ink-soft);
}
ol.steps li:last-child{border-bottom:0}
ol.steps li::before{
  content:counter(step);flex-shrink:0;width:25px;height:25px;border-radius:8px;
  background:var(--teal-soft);border:1px solid rgba(29,158,117,.25);
  font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--teal-deep);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-top:1px;
}
ol.steps li strong{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}
code.key{
  font-family:ui-monospace,'SF Mono',Menlo,monospace;font-size:13px;
  background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:5px;
  padding:1px 6px;color:var(--teal-deep);
}

.spam-note{
  display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;
  background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:12px;
  padding:14px 16px;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:28px;
}
.spam-note svg{width:18px;height:18px;stroke:var(--gold);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.spam-note strong{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}

.footer{
  display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;
  padding-top:22px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);
}
.footer a{
  color:var(--ink-soft);text-decoration:none;font-size:13.5px;
  border-bottom:1px solid transparent;transition:color .15s,border-color .15s;
}
.footer a:hover{color:var(--teal-deep);border-bottom-color:var(--teal-deep)}
.brand{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--muted)}
.brand a{color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none}
.brand a:hover{color:var(--ink-soft)}

@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.card{animation:none}.status-dot{animation:none}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="card" role="main">
    <div class="eyebrow"><span class="status-dot"></span>Payment confirmed</div>

    <div class="check" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
    </div>

    <h1 class="display">Thanks for upgrading to DocKit Pro</h1>
    <p class="lede">Your payment went through. Your license key is on its way to your inbox right now — here's how to unlock every Pro tool.</p>

    <div class="steps-label">Activate in 3 steps</div>
    <ol class="steps">
      <li><span>Open the email from DocKit and copy your key — it looks like <code class="key">dk-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX</code>.</span></li>
      <li><span>In DocKit, click <strong>Upgrade to Pro</strong>, then <strong>I have a key</strong>.</span></li>
      <li><span>Paste the key and click <strong>Activate</strong>. Every Pro tool unlocks instantly — still 100% on your device.</span></li>
    </ol>

    <div class="spam-note">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4z"/><path d="m4 7 8 6 8-6"/></svg>
      <span><strong>Don't see the email?</strong> Give it a minute, then check your spam or promotions folder — it sometimes lands there. Still nothing after a few minutes? Email us and we'll sort it straight away.</span>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <a href="mailto:hello@niallcodes.com">Need help? hello@niallcodes.com</a>
      <span class="brand"><a href="https://niallcodes.com">niallcodes</a></span>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
